---
/**
 * ResponsibleGamblingCTA Component
 * Single Responsibility: Promote responsible gambling resources and self-exclusion tools
 */
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-900/20 to-orange-900/20 border-t-4 border-red-500" id="responsible-gambling">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🛑</div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Gamble Responsibly</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
          Gambling should be fun. If it's not, we're here to help.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-10">
        <!-- Set Limits -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-red-500/30">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">⏰</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Set Limits</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
            Set deposit, loss, and time limits before you play. All our recommended casinos offer limit-setting tools.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Know the Signs -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-red-500/30">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">⚠️</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Know the Signs</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
            Chasing losses, hiding gambling habits, or neglecting responsibilities? These are warning signs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Get Help -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-red-500/30">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Get Help</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
            Free, confidential support is available 24/7. You're not alone.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Help Resources -->
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 text-center">Support Organizations</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="text-2xl mr-3">🇨🇦</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Canada</h4>
                <a href="https://www.responsiblegambling.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 text-sm">
                  Responsible Gambling Council
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="text-2xl mr-3">🇺🇸</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">USA</h4>
                <a href="https://www.ncpgambling.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 text-sm">
                  National Council on Problem Gambling
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="text-2xl mr-3">🇬🇧</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">UK</h4>
                <a href="https://www.begambleaware.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 text-sm">
                  BeGambleAware
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="text-2xl mr-3">🌍</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">International</h4>
                <a href="https://www.gamblersanonymous.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 text-sm">
                  Gamblers Anonymous
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="text-2xl mr-3">🔒</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Self-Exclusion</h4>
                <a href="https://www.gamstop.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 text-sm">
                  GamStop (UK)
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="text-2xl mr-3">📞</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">24/7 Helpline</h4>
                <a href="tel:1-800-522-4700" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 text-sm font-mono">
                  1-800-522-4700
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Points -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Remember:</h3>
        <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-gray-300 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Gambling is entertainment, not a way to make money</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Never gamble with money you can't afford to lose</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Set a budget and stick to it</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Take regular breaks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Never chase losses</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Don't gamble when upset or under the influence</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Legal Age Notice -->
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-lg">🔞 You must be 18+ or 19+ (depending on region) to gamble</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2">Underage gambling is illegal and harmful</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
